        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
            <ul class="difference-list">
                <li><strong>No sponsored content:</strong> We don't accept payment for positive reviews. Our opinions are genuinely ours.</li>
                <li><strong>Real-world testing:</strong> We use products in actual parenting situations, not just in controlled environments.</li>
                <li><strong>Long-term perspective:</strong> We consider how products perform over months and years, not just initial impressions.</li>
                <li><strong>Budget-conscious:</strong> We understand that parenting is expensive. We help you find value, not just premium products.</li>
                <li><strong>Safety first:</strong> Every recommendation meets current safety standards and best practices.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Promise to You</h2>
            <p>We promise to:</p>
            <ul class="promise-list">
                <li>Always be honest about product limitations and drawbacks</li>
                <li>Update our recommendations as new information becomes available</li>
                <li>Focus on products that genuinely help parents and children</li>
                <li>Respect your time with clear, actionable advice</li>
                <li>Maintain our independence from product manufacturers</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
            <p>We're transparent about our business model. We earn small commissions when you purchase products through our affiliate links. This doesn't cost you anything extra, but it helps us continue researching and reviewing products.</p>
            
            <p>Our affiliate relationships never influence our recommendations. We recommend products we genuinely believe in, regardless of commission rates. You can read more about this in our <a href="{{ '/affiliate-disclosure.html' | relative_url }}">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.</p>
        </section>

